                <xsl:when test="/Root/MultiEpisodeOutcomeStructure/WorkerCodes/ArrayNode"><xsl:for-each select="/Root/MultiEpisodeOutcomeStructure/WorkerCodes/ArrayNode"><xsl:value-of select="ItemValue"/>:<xsl:value-of select="ItemDescription"/>*</xsl:for-each>
